data.description: Are you ready to start your new year in your next home?!?! Seller to credit buyer $2,000 (two thousand dollars) at closing to be used towards closing costs. Welcome to your new chapter in this Ranch style home! With 4 beds, 3 baths, a fenced backyard, and a finished basement, it's perfect for new memories. Do you love breath taking views? This home is located only 34 mins from Glacier National Park and 20 mins from Flathead Lake! Montana Means Home, Call Sergio Gallegos 406.871.7662 or Rebecca Gallegos 406.499.1275, or your real estate professional to schedule a showing.
